query:
SELECT 
  p.id,
  s.name as service_name,
  c.name as country_name,
  a.id as api_id,
  a.name as api_name,
  p.ourPrice
FROM prices p
INNER JOIN services s ON p.serviceId = s.id
INNER JOIN countries c ON p.countryId = c.id
INNER JOIN sms_apis a ON p.apiId = a.id
WHERE a.active = 1
LIMIT 10;
